data.description: Handyman special with lots of potential in West Mobile! This home is ready for your special touch. It is perfect for either an investor or first-time homebuyer with a renovation loan. This home features 3 bedrooms and 2 full baths. The private backyard is perfect for parties, cookouts, or for families events. Laundry room contains shelving for storage. Conveniently located close to shopping, stores, airport, Municipal Park, and the University of South Alabama. Per the seller some repairs have been made to the roof back in January 2023 due to a leak in the master bath. Buyer or buyer's agent to verify all information. Home is sold "AS-IS" and seller makes no warranties.
